    <div class="body prose twelve columns" itemprop="body articleBody">
        <p>Australian-American inventor Saul Griffith has started seven companies, among them Makani Power, for which he invented an eco-friendly, efficient wind turbine. He received a MacArthur Grant in 2007.</p>

        
    </div>

    
    

